{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-tutorial/c1/1.3"},"id":"5affd0ae-82b7-5406-9e5a-f35566dfcb12","html":"<h2 id=\"13使用graphql解析markdown\"><a href=\"#13%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8graphql%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90markdown\" aria-label=\"13使用graphql解析markdown permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.3使用GraphQL解析Markdown</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1什么是graphql\"><a href=\"#1%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AFgraphql\" aria-label=\"1什么是graphql permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.什么是GraphQL</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>GraphQL 既是一种用于 API 的查询语言也是一个满足你数据查询的运行时。 GraphQL 对你的 API 中的数据提供了一套易于理解的完整描述，使得客户端能够准确地获得它需要的数据，而且没有任何冗余，也让 API 更容易地随着时间推移而演进，还能用于构建强大的开发者工具。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>官网：<a href=\"http://graphql.cn/\">http://graphql.cn/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"2为什么需要它？\"><a href=\"#2%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%AE%83%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"2为什么需要它？ permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.为什么需要它？</h3>\n<p>一图抵万言：</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/54af6/1557045421223.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 78.31325301204821%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"1557045421223\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/b9e4f/1557045421223.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/cf440/1557045421223.png 148w,\n/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/d2d38/1557045421223.png 295w,\n/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/b9e4f/1557045421223.png 590w,\n/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/f9b6a/1557045421223.png 885w,\n/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/2d849/1557045421223.png 1180w,\n/static/c48df1db0e05716d47fa4eb54898b2ab/54af6/1557045421223.png 1245w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"3怎么做？\"><a href=\"#3%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%81%9A%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"3怎么做？ permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3.怎么做？</h3>\n<h4 id=\"1一图抵万言，\"><a href=\"#1%E4%B8%80%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%B5%E4%B8%87%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%8C\" aria-label=\"1一图抵万言， permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.一图抵万言，</h4>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/76706/1557046295168.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 28.968253968253965%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"1557046295168\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/b9e4f/1557046295168.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/cf440/1557046295168.png 148w,\n/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/d2d38/1557046295168.png 295w,\n/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/b9e4f/1557046295168.png 590w,\n/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/f9b6a/1557046295168.png 885w,\n/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/2d849/1557046295168.png 1180w,\n/static/6eea46c520022ef826f5419f632cdd7c/76706/1557046295168.png 1764w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>解释：你需要的东西都在这段代码里：</p>\n<pre><code>{\n  site {\n    siteMetadata {\n      title\n    }\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"2怎么套到组件里？\"><a href=\"#2%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%A5%97%E5%88%B0%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"2怎么套到组件里？ permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.怎么套到组件里？</h4>\n<p>src>components>Header.js里面，</p>\n<pre><code>import { StaticQuery, graphql } from 'gatsby'\nimport React from \"react\"\nconst TitleAndDescription = ({ data }) => {\n//这里的数据是下面查出来的\n  const title = data.site.siteMetadata.title;\n  const description = data.site.siteMetadata.description;\n  return (\n    &#x3C;div style={{\n      display: 'flex',\n      flexDirection: 'column',\n      alignItems: 'center'\n    }}>\n      &#x3C;h2>{title}&#x3C;/h2>\n      &#x3C;p>{description}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;/div>\n  );\n}\n//这里是所有数据，传到了TitleAndDescription组件里，react组件数据传递\nconst Header = () => {\n  return (\n    &#x3C;StaticQuery\n      query={graphql`\n        query{\n          site {\n            siteMetadata {\n              title,\n              description,\n              \n            }\n          }\n        }\n      `}\n      render={data => &#x3C;TitleAndDescription data={data} />}\n    />\n  )\n}\nexport default Header\n</code></pre>\n<p>这里是所有数据，传到了TitleAndDescription组件里，react组件数据传递,我这么就为了看着舒服一点。</p>\n<h4 id=\"3嵌套header\"><a href=\"#3%E5%B5%8C%E5%A5%97header\" aria-label=\"3嵌套header permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3.嵌套Header</h4>\n<p>将Header组件扔到 pages下面的index.js里面：</p>\n<pre><code>import React from \"react\"\nimport Header from '../components/header'\nconst Layout = () => {\n  return (\n    &#x3C;div>\n      &#x3C;Header />\n    &#x3C;/div>\n  )\n}\nexport default Layout;\n</code></pre>\n<p>打开首页，看到网站的描述就大功告成了。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":null,"title":"1.3使用GraphQL解析Markdown","root":"/gatsby-tutorial"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false}}